Class ElectronicResourceTest

java.lang.Object
ElectronicResourceTest
public class ElectronicResourceTest extends Object
Unit tests for the ElectronicResource class.

Tests the functionality of the constructor, getter, setter, and getDetails methods. Implicitly tests the printDetails method as it just applies System.out.println to the getDetails method.
